OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781039474
OL,3,CTrump says pilots are 'fine' after US
OL,4,Chelicopter crashes near Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FA US Army Apache attack helicopter has
OL,8,Fcrashed near the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,9,Fwith US President Donald Trump saying
OL,10,Fthe two crew members abroad were
OL,11,F"fine" after the incident.
OL,13,FWhat caused the crash remained unclear
OL,14,Fon Tuesday morning in the Middle East,
OL,15,Fwhich was still reeling after Iran and
OL,16,FIsrael exchanged fire the previous day
OL,17,Fin the biggest blow yet to the
OL,18,Fstraining ceasefire in the Iran war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
