OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781039474
OL,3,CTrump says pilots are 'fine' after US
OL,4,Chelicopter crashes near Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FTrump, speaking to journalists at John
OL,8,FF. Kennedy International Airport in
OL,9,FNew York after watching the NBA Finals
OL,10,Fon Monday night, acknowledged the
OL,11,Fcrash.
OL,13,F"The pilots are fine. Yeah," Trump
OL,14,Fsaid. "Nobody injured. We are going to
OL,15,Fissue a report tomorrow. But the
OL,16,Fpilots are fine."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
