OL,3,CTrump says pilots are 'fine' after US
OL,4,Chelicopter crashes near Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe New York Times first reported that
OL,8,Fa U.S. Army Apache attack helicopter
OL,9,Fwent down near the strait in unclear
OL,10,Fcircumstances. The US military's
OL,11,FCentral Command and the Defense
OL,12,FDepartment did not immediately respond
OL,13,Fto requests for comment from The
OL,14,FAssociated Press.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
