OL,3,CTrump says pilots are 'fine' after US
OL,4,Chelicopter crashes near Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FApache helicopters have been a key
OL,8,Fasset for the American military as it
OL,9,Fenforces a blockade on Iranian crude
OL,10,Foil shipments and tankers, seeking to
OL,11,Fpressure Tehran into reaching a deal.
OL,12,FThe helicopters also have been used by
OL,13,Fthe United Arab Emirates to shoot down
OL,14,FIranian drones during the Iran war.
OL,16,FTrump also expressed renewed optimism
OL,17,Fover negotiations with Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
