OL,3,CTrump says pilots are 'fine' after US
OL,4,Chelicopter crashes near Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,F"We have a good chance" of signing a
OL,13,Fdeal in "two or three days," Trump
OL,14,Fsaid. But he didn't provide any
OL,15,Fdetails on why there was reason for
OL,16,Fnew optimism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
