OL,3,CTrump says pilots are 'fine' after US
OL,4,Chelicopter crashes near Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,F"We're very close to having a very,
OL,8,Fvery good, strong, powerful deal," the
OL,9,Fpresident said. "If we go and bomb -
OL,10,Fwhich we could do very easily if we
OL,11,Fwant, and we spend another two or
OL,12,Fthree weeks bombing - they'll have
OL,13,Fnothing left whatsoever. But you won't
OL,14,Fhave the strait open for months."
OL,16,FHe added: "If we do the bombing, you
OL,17,Fknow, a lot of people are going to be
OL,18,Fkilled. Who wants to do that? I don't."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
