OL,3,CTrump says pilots are 'fine' after US
OL,4,Chelicopter crashes near Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FMediators, led predominantly by
OL,8,FPakistan, have been trying to weeks to
OL,9,Fget a deal across the line. However,
OL,10,Fboth Iran and the U.S. have taken hard-
OL,11,Fline positions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
