OL,3,CTrump says pilots are 'fine' after US
OL,4,Chelicopter crashes near Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz
OL,7,FThe US wants to see Iran give up its
OL,8,Fstockpile of highly enriched uranium,
OL,9,Fwhich is believed still to be entombed
OL,10,Fin the country after American
OL,11,Fairstrikes in the 12-day war in 2025.
OL,12,FBut Iran is refusing that and
OL,13,Fdemanding relief from sanctions. It
OL,14,Falso wants the release of frozen
OL,15,Fassets even before a final agreement
OL,16,Fis in place, something rejected by
OL,17,FTrump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
